h, and Huw David for the scrutiny session.&#10;6. Members will discuss and ask questions regarding the explanatory memorandum that accompanies the Bill, focusing on unidentified costs for different agencies.&#10;7. Members will discuss implementation for social services, including potential increases in referrals to social services and the police, decision-making processes, and resource allocation.">
