at he is not a legislator or lawyer and therefore cannot comment on its implications.&#10;3. Sally Jenkins from the Association of Directors of Social Services (ADSS) does not think it is essential for this duty to be included in the text of the Bill. Instead, she advocates for discussions on nuancing during the implementation phase. She emphasizes the importance of simplicity and clarity to avoid further confusion.&#10;4. Lynne Neagle AM thanks Sian Gwenllian AM for her question and moves on to discuss other aspects of the meeting.">
