sues related to adverse childhood experiences.&#10;&#10;Sally Jenkins also mentions that there could be positive unintended consequences, such as reinvigorating discussions around the voice of the child within various contexts. She does not think that this Bill is a way of getting money into social services; instead, it is about reinforcing the commitment to children's rights and promoting their well-being in Wales.">
